{"word":"ἀχθεινός","slug":"ἀχθεινός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀχθεινός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἄχθος'><el>ἄχθος</el></a>\n<p/><i>burdensome, oppressive, wearisome</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>molestus</el>, of persons, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-νῶς</el>, <i>unwillingly</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}